<br>
Some of the parts of the druid epic can be done for multiple druids in a short time.  For instance, we need to get a group together and kill a corrupted cyclops on seafury island in oot.  While we have a group together, we could probably get decent experience and get several pieces for epics in a short amount of time.  Which brings me to another thing, a lot of these parts are either good experience or short in duration, so everyone should be able to benefit even if not out of the you-scratch-my-back-I'll-scratch-yours phenomenon.<br>
<br>
I'm about ready to kill our old friend the dark elf corruptor, which (I'll have to ask around about this) can probably be taken with 3 upper level druids and a tank.  Hopefully I won't kill my neriak faction too badly <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br>
<br>
Anyhow, this is just meant to see who is interested in starting epics or other such quests, and giving and receiving help.<br>
<br>
